{%- doc -%}
  Default legal policy copy for Luxe Leaf Tea when Shopify admin policies are empty.
  Paste the matching section into Settings → Policies to customize, or leave blank to use these defaults.
{%- enddoc -%}

{%- liquid
  assign free_ship_cents = settings.free_shipping_threshold | default: 5000
  assign standard_ship_cents = settings.standard_shipping_rate | default: 595
  assign free_ship_label = free_ship_cents | money
  assign standard_ship_label = standard_ship_cents | money

  assign support_email = settings.brand_email
  if support_email == blank
    assign support_email = shop.email
  endif

  assign contact_url = pages['contact'].url | default: '/pages/contact'
-%}

{%- case policy_kind -%}
  {%- when 'privacy' -%}
    <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> {{ 'now' | date: '%B %d, %Y' }}</p>
    <p>{{ shop.name }} ("we," "us," or "our") respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect personal information when you visit {{ shop.url }} or purchase premium loose leaf tea from our online store.</p>

    <h2>Information we collect</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Order information:</strong> name, shipping address, billing address, email, phone (if provided), and payment details processed securely by Shopify.</li>
      <li><strong>Account information:</strong> if you create an account, we store your login email and order history.</li>
      <li><strong>Marketing:</strong> if you join our email list, we store your email address and subscription preferences.</li>
      <li><strong>Support messages:</strong> information you send when contacting us or using our Tea Guide chat.</li>
      <li><strong>Usage data:</strong> device, browser, and analytics data collected through cookies and similar technologies (see below).</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How we use information</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Fulfill and ship your orders, including packed-fresh fulfillment and tracking updates.</li>
      <li>Process payments and prevent fraud.</li>
      <li>Respond to questions about tea, orders, and brewing.</li>
      <li>Send marketing emails you opt into (you may unsubscribe anytime).</li>
      <li>Improve our website, products, and customer experience.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Sharing</h2>
    <p>We do not sell your personal information. We share data only with service providers who help us operate our store (for example Shopify, payment processors, shipping carriers, and email providers) under appropriate confidentiality obligations, or when required by law.</p>

    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>We use cookies and similar technologies for essential site functions, cart persistence, analytics, and marketing (where permitted). You can control cookies through your browser settings.</p>

    <h2>Your choices</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Opt out of marketing emails using the unsubscribe link in any message.</li>
      <li>Request access, correction, or deletion of personal information by contacting us.</li>
      <li>Disable cookies in your browser (some site features may not work).</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data retention</h2>
    <p>We retain order and account records as needed to fulfill orders, comply with law, and resolve disputes.</p>

    <h2>Children</h2>
    <p>Our store is not directed to children under 13, and we do not knowingly collect their personal information.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions about this Privacy Policy? Email <a href="mailto:{{ support_email | escape }}">{{ support_email }}</a> or visit our <a href="{{ contact_url }}">contact page</a>.</p>

  {%- when 'terms' -%}
    <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> {{ 'now' | date: '%B %d, %Y' }}</p>
    <p>These Terms of Service ("Terms") govern your use of {{ shop.url }} and purchases from {{ shop.name }}. By accessing our site or placing an order, you agree to these Terms.</p>

    <h2>Eligibility</h2>
    <p>You must be at least the age of majority in your jurisdiction to purchase tea products from our store.</p>

    <h2>Products &amp; pricing</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>We sell premium loose leaf tea and related products. Descriptions, origin notes, and images are accurate to the best of our knowledge but natural variation in harvests may occur.</li>
      <li>Prices are shown in the currency displayed at checkout and may change without notice.</li>
      <li>We reserve the right to limit quantities or refuse orders placed in error or in violation of these Terms.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Orders &amp; payment</h2>
    <p>When you place an order, you offer to purchase products subject to these Terms. We may confirm, decline, or cancel orders (for example due to inventory, payment issues, or suspected fraud). Payment is processed securely through Shopify.</p>

    <h2>Fresh packing</h2>
    <p>Tea is packed fresh after you order. Processing time is typically 1–2 business days before shipment unless otherwise stated at checkout.</p>

    <h2>Intellectual property</h2>
    <p>All content on this site — including text, photos, logos, and brewing guides — is owned by {{ shop.name }} or our licensors and may not be copied or reused without permission.</p>

    <h2>Disclaimer</h2>
    <p>Tea is a food product for personal consumption. Brewing guidance is educational and not medical advice. Our site and products are provided "as is" to the fullest extent permitted by law.</p>

    <h2>Limitation of liability</h2>
    <p>To the maximum extent permitted by law, {{ shop.name }} is not liable for indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from your use of the site or products. Our total liability for any claim related to an order is limited to the amount you paid for that order.</p>

    <h2>Governing law</h2>
    <p>These Terms are governed by the laws applicable where {{ shop.name }} operates, without regard to conflict-of-law rules.</p>

    <h2>Changes</h2>
    <p>We may update these Terms from time to time. Continued use of the site after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated Terms.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions? Email <a href="mailto:{{ support_email | escape }}">{{ support_email }}</a> or visit our <a href="{{ contact_url }}">contact page</a>.</p>

  {%- when 'refund' -%}
    <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> {{ 'now' | date: '%B %d, %Y' }}</p>
    <p>We want every cup to feel worth slowing down for. If something isn't right with your order, contact us and we'll make it right.</p>

    <h2>Freshness guarantee</h2>
    <p>Premium loose leaf tea is packed fresh after you order. If your tea arrives damaged, defective, or not as described, contact us within <strong>14 days of delivery</strong> with your order number and photos if applicable.</p>

    <h2>Eligible returns &amp; refunds</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Items damaged in transit or fulfillment errors.</li>
      <li>Incorrect items shipped.</li>
      <li>Quality concerns with an unopened or minimally sampled product — we'll work with you case by case.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Non-returnable items</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Opened tea that has been substantially used, except when quality issues are reported promptly.</li>
      <li>Gift cards and digital products.</li>
      <li>Final sale items marked as non-returnable at purchase.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How to request help</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Email <a href="mailto:{{ support_email | escape }}">{{ support_email }}</a> or use our <a href="{{ contact_url }}">contact page</a> with your order number.</li>
      <li>Tell us what happened — we'll respond within 1 business day.</li>
      <li>If a return is approved, we'll provide instructions. Refunds are issued to the original payment method after we receive and inspect returned items (if applicable).</li>
    </ol>

    <h2>Refund timing</h2>
    <p>Approved refunds are processed within 5–10 business days. Your bank may take additional time to post the credit.</p>

    <h2>Exchanges</h2>
    <p>Prefer a different tea? Contact us — we're happy to recommend a better match or arrange an exchange when possible.</p>

  {%- when 'shipping' -%}
    <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> {{ 'now' | date: '%B %d, %Y' }}</p>
    <p>We pack premium loose leaf tea fresh after you order and ship to addresses within our service areas.</p>

    <h2>Processing time</h2>
    <p>Orders are typically packed within <strong>1–2 business days</strong> (Monday–Friday, excluding holidays). You'll receive a shipping confirmation with tracking when your tea leaves our tea room.</p>

    <h2>Shipping rates</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Free standard shipping</strong> on orders of {{ free_ship_label }} or more (before tax, after discounts, where applicable).</li>
      <li>Orders below {{ free_ship_label }}: standard shipping from {{ standard_ship_label }} — exact rates shown at checkout before you pay.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Delivery estimates</h2>
    <p>After shipment, standard delivery is typically <strong>3–7 business days</strong> within the contiguous United States. Remote areas, weather, and carrier delays may extend transit time.</p>

    <h2>Order tracking</h2>
    <p>Tracking is emailed when your order ships. Allow 24 hours for the carrier to scan your package.</p>

    <h2>Incorrect addresses</h2>
    <p>Please verify your shipping address at checkout. We cannot redirect packages once shipped and are not responsible for delays caused by incorrect addresses.</p>

    <h2>Lost or damaged packages</h2>
    <p>If tracking shows delivered but you didn't receive your tea, or if your order arrives damaged, contact us within 7 days at <a href="mailto:{{ support_email | escape }}">{{ support_email }}</a>.</p>

    <h2>International shipping</h2>
    <p>International availability, duties, and taxes (if any) are shown at checkout. Customers are responsible for import fees where applicable.</p>

  {%- else -%}
    <p>Policy content for {{ shop.name }}. Configure this policy in Shopify admin under <strong>Settings → Policies</strong>, or contact us at <a href="mailto:{{ support_email | escape }}">{{ support_email }}</a>.</p>
{%- endcase -%}
